info.description:
### Prerequisites

- Postman
- AI21 Labs Account: [https://studio.ai21.com/](https://studio.ai21.com/)
    

### Usage

1. Create a fork
2. Update collection variables
3. Send requests
    

### Documentation

- API: [https://docs.ai21.com/reference](https://docs.ai21.com/reference)
- Models: [https://studio.ai21.com/models](https://studio.ai21.com/models)
    

### About AI21 Labs

AI lab & product company whose mission is to reimagine the way we read and write by making the machine a thought partner to humans.
